    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "Offered for sale is a fair-condition driver that would suit someone looking for an affordable, usable car rather than a fully sorted or show-ready example. It shows visible age and wear in the paint, interior, and overall presentation, and buyers should expect cosmetic imperfections consistent with a car that has been used over the years. That said, it still presents as a straightforward, honest example for someone who values practicality and value over perfection. A sensible choice for a buyer wanting an entry-level car with room to improve over time.",
