    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Value-priced and ready for its next chapter, this vehicle is a practical choice for buyers seeking affordable transportation or a solid project opportunity. It shows clear signs of age and wear, and is being offered with straightforward, transparent positioning. For the right buyer, it presents an accessible way to get behind the wheel without a major investment.",
