      "timestep_posted": 34
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for honest, affordable wheels? This car isn\u2019t pretending to be showroom fresh, but it\u2019s a solid budget-friendly option for someone who wants dependable transportation without spending a fortune. It\u2019s got character, it\u2019s priced right, and it could make a great runaround, first car, or little project for the right person. If you want something cheap, straightforward, and easy on the wallet, this one is well worth a look.",
      "price": 5950.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 34
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Solid project or budget daily with a willing powertrain, responsive steering feel, and a drivetrain that still pulls cleanly through the rev range. Starts, runs, and moves, with the kind of mechanical honesty enthusiasts appreciate. Cosmetic wear and general rough-around-the-edges condition are present, but the car has good bones, a usable cabin, and plenty of upside for someone who wants an affordable platform to drive as-is, sort out, or build further. Priced to move for the next owner who knows what they\u2019re looking at.",
      "price": 7900.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
