    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "A diamond-in-the-rough with real presence, this car has the kind of character you just don\u2019t find in cookie-cutter commuters. It\u2019s an honest, old-school ride with a story in its bones\u2014perfect for someone who appreciates potential, wants a budget-friendly runabout, or is looking for a rewarding project. Whether you\u2019re after a practical spare vehicle, a hands-on tinkering opportunity, or simply something with personality, this one offers an affordable way to get into a car with undeniable spirit.",
      "price": 5900.0,
