      "timestep_posted": 34
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Budget-friendly and ready for its next chapter, this vehicle is a practical choice for someone seeking affordable transportation, a project, or a dependable parts donor. It shows clear signs of age and wear, but it still offers solid value at an accessible price. If you want an inexpensive option with potential and prefer a straightforward purchase, this one is worth a look.",
