      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Looking for a cheap set of wheels or a straightforward project? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s an honest budget option with plenty of potential for someone handy or just needing basic transport without spending a fortune. It shows its age and will suit a buyer who knows what a used car in this kind of shape is all about, but at this price it\u2019s a great chance to get into something affordable. Priced to sell and worth a look if you want value over flash.",
